mpted=yes }}, by Inti Landauro, ''Fox Business'', June 27, 2011, Retrieved October 2, 2011.</ref> || [[Turkey]] || Pension and Life Insurance\n|}\n\n===Companies sold===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Name of Company !! Country !! Industry\n|-\n| Deniz T\u00fcrev Menkul De\u011ferler A.\u015e.<ref>[https://www.reuters.com/finance/stocks/DENIZ.IS/key-developments/article/2367092 \"Denizbank A.S. Sells Deniz Turev Menkul Degerler A.S.\"], by Reuters Ticker, ''Reuters'' U.S. Edition, July 20, 2011, Retrieved October 2, 2011.</ref> || [[Turkey]] || Securities\n|}\n\n==Products and services==\n* Retail banking\n* Private banking\n* Business banking\n* Agricultural banking\n* Corporate banking\n* Commercial banking\n* Public finance<ref name=\"DenizBankRef001\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.denizbank.com/EN/AboutUs/|title=DenizBank A.\u015e. About Us|publisher=DenizBank A.\u015e.}}</ref>\n<!-- Deleted image removed: [[File:DenizBank HQ PhotoPressKit.jpg|thumb|DenizBank A.\u015e. Headquarter Building in [[Istanbul]]]] -->\n<!-- Deleted image removed: [[File:DenizBankCEOHakanAtes.jpg|thumb|DenizBank A.\u015e. CEO Mr. Hakan Ate\u015f]] -->\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of banks in Turkey]]\n*[[List of Turkish companies]]\n\n==References==\n<references/>\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n*{{Official|http://www.denizbank.com/ }}\n*[http://www.dexia.com/ Group Dexia official website]\n*[http://www.denizyatirim.com/ DenizYat\u0131r\u0131m Menkul K\u0131ymetler A.\u015e. (Deniz Investment Securities)] (in Turkish, with English language available)\n*[http://www.denizbank.at/ DenizBank AG] (in German)\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20110904032105/http://www.ekspresinvest.com.tr/ EkspresInvest Menkul K\u0131ymetler A.\u015e.] (in English)\n*[http://www.dexiabank.ru/ CJSC Dexia Bank Russia] (in English)\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20110222014338/http://www.denizemeklilik.com.tr/ Deniz Emeklilik ve Hayat A.\u015e. (Deniz Pension and Life Insurance)] (in Turkish only)\n*[https://w